76561198003696194,Recommended,282210,14910132,"Posted: 15 March, 2015",all,KaldariaQ,"Fun little twist on typical 4x thinking.  I like how you dont ""build"" ships that then become obsolete.  Every ship can be upgraded indivitually and once you own the frame of the ship even if it dies in battle it will respawn.  The assumption is that when its reduced to 0hp it just leaves the battle or something.  Going dark is plausable in a space game.Upgrades and reserch is instant so you can focus on racing around the galaxy brining planets under your federation.Recommend if you like new ideas and fun tactial space battles.  Dont reccomend if you demand high depth in every 4X game you play cause this one is on the light side."
